ALL PRACTICE AREAS



 


 




For 30 years GLG has excelled in a full range of immigrations services to corporations and individuals throughout the world. Founding partner, David Garfield, is recognized by the Washingtonian Magazine as a top immigration attorney. Our experienced and diverse staff has successfully represented a broad range of clientele; from billion dollar corporations to refugees fleeing from violence and persecution. Our attorneys travel throughout the United States and overseas to advocate passionately for our clients. With an office in Honolulu, Hawaii, and a partnership with a respected Vietnamese law firm (ATS), GLG is well positioned to engage clients from Asia and the Pacific Rim.




 



 

 







