Marijuana Business Law

McAllister Garfield, P.C. helped draft Colorado’s recreational legalization law and has represented hundreds of dispensaries and cannabis companies since 2009. McAllister Garfield, P.C. represents some of the national leading marijuana companies and is a full service business law firm for the marijuana industry.
 

